WEBVTT

00:10.300 --> 00:11.340
CHAPTER XVII.

00:11.600 --> 00:13.400
SUMMARY OF THE SCIENCE OF GETTING RICH

00:14.240 --> 00:19.560
There is a thinking stuff from which all things are made, and which, in its original state,

00:19.840 --> 00:23.300
permeates, penetrates, and fills the interspaces of the universe.

00:24.040 --> 00:28.160
A thought in this substance produces the thing that is imaged by the thought.

00:28.160 --> 00:33.940
Man can form things in his thought, and by impressing his thought upon formless substance

00:33.940 --> 00:36.980
can cause the thing he thinks about to be created.

00:37.500 --> 00:42.560
In order to do this, man must pass from the competitive to the creative mind, otherwise

00:42.560 --> 00:46.900
he cannot be in harmony with the formless intelligence, which is always creative and

00:46.900 --> 00:48.620
never competitive in spirit.

00:49.340 --> 00:54.340
Man may come into full harmony with the formless substance by entertaining a lively and sincere

00:54.340 --> 00:57.140
gratitude for the blessings it bestows upon him.

00:57.140 --> 01:02.360
Gratitude unifies the mind of man with the intelligence of substance, so that man's

01:02.360 --> 01:04.460
thoughts are received by the formless.

01:05.040 --> 01:09.860
Man can remain upon the creative plane only by uniting himself with the formless intelligence

01:09.860 --> 01:12.840
through a deep and continuous feeling of gratitude.

01:13.620 --> 01:18.140
Man must form a clear and definite mental image of the things he wishes to have, to

01:18.140 --> 01:23.600
do, or to become, and he must hold this mental image in his thoughts while being deeply grateful

01:23.600 --> 01:26.900
to the Supreme that all he desires are granted to him.

01:27.580 --> 01:32.420
The man who wishes to get rich must spend his leisure hours in contemplating his vision,

01:32.760 --> 01:36.760
and in earnest thanksgiving that the reality is being given to him.

01:37.200 --> 01:42.020
Too much stress cannot be laid on the importance of frequent contemplation of the mental image

01:42.020 --> 01:45.380
coupled with unwavering faith and devout gratitude.

01:45.960 --> 01:50.140
This is the process by which the impression is given to the formless and the creative

01:50.140 --> 01:51.640
forces set in motion.

01:52.400 --> 01:57.160
The creative energy works through the established channels of natural growth and of the industrial

01:57.160 --> 01:58.240
and social order.

01:58.940 --> 02:03.500
All that is included in his mental image will surely be brought to the man who follows the

02:03.500 --> 02:07.060
instructions given above, and whose faith does not waver.

02:07.600 --> 02:11.700
What he wants will come to him through the ways of established trade and commerce.

02:12.420 --> 02:17.440
In order to receive his own when it shall come to him, man must be active, and this

02:17.440 --> 02:20.840
activity can only consist in more than filling his present place.

02:20.840 --> 02:26.120
He must keep in mind the purpose to get rich through the realization of his mental image,

02:26.520 --> 02:31.600
and he must do, every day, all that can be done that day, taking care to do each act

02:31.600 --> 02:32.840
in a successful manner.

02:33.260 --> 02:38.500
He must give to every man a use-value in excess of the cash-value he receives, so that each

02:38.500 --> 02:43.860
transaction makes for more life, and he must so hold the advancing thought that the impression

02:43.860 --> 02:47.460
of increase will be communicated to all with whom he comes in contact.

02:48.100 --> 02:53.380
The men and women who practice the foregoing instructions will certainly get rich, and

02:53.380 --> 02:58.560
the riches they receive will be in exact proportion to the definiteness of their vision, the fixity

02:58.560 --> 03:03.080
of their purpose, the steadiness of their faith, and the depth of their gratitude.

